item.title: the start of my rambling on
item.description: In the big wide world of technology its impossible not to spent your time learning. Im often learning, testing, breaking or doing something that I never document. This is my attempt to capture what I’ve learnt (am learning) and learn even more. Wordpress was fun back in the day for a single post. Only time will tell this is any better…
